    import './index.scss'

    const AnimatedLetters = ({ letterClass, strArray, idx }) => {
    return (
    <span>
    {strArray.map((char, i) => (
    <span key={char + i} className={`${letterClass} _${i + idx}`}>
    {char}
    </span>
    ))}
    </span>
    )
    }

    export default AnimatedLetters
